Urls of my api - 

base url - http://localhost:3000/

Resources - 

1) GET /blogs 		- this is used to get all blogs - array of objects

2) GET /blog/:Id 	- this is used to get the info of a particular blog. ID is the variable - 						
					  output : object of particular Id

3) POST /blog/create	- create a blog ,
						Input required - title, subTitle, blogBody, author ,tags : title should be unique
						output - object of created blog


4) PUT /blog/edit/:id - edit a blog, 
						Input required - title, subTitle, blogBody, author ,tags : title should be unique
						output - object of updated blog


5) POST /blog/delete/:id - remove a blog 
							output - msg: blog deleted

6) POST /blog/comment/:id - comment on blog 
							Input required - commentorName ,commentBody ,timendate
							output - object of commented blog
